{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343700/extras/AnimatedLogo.gif?t=1681847013\" /></h2><br><br><strong><i>Spirit of the Backwaters is a rural life-sim with farming and some management elements. You'll play as a budding entrepreneur who's tasked with running and managing the local toddy shop. Turn it into a cash cow or a quaint little hideaway that serves nothing short of the finest quality toddy. The choice is yours!</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343700/extras/ToddyWho.png?t=1681847013\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343700/extras/Shibu_Toddy.gif?t=1681847013\" /></h2><br><br><i>Toddy</i> is a mildly alcoholic drink made from the sap of coconut trees and is known by different names around the world. It's more than just a drink \u2013 it's an integral part of local cuisine and community celebrations.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343700/extras/Tap_Brew.png?t=1681847013\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343700/extras/Tapping.gif?t=1681847013\" /></h2><br><br>Navigate obstacles like insects and bad weather to supply the toddy shop with the required amount of quality toddy every business day. Using higher quality tools and materials yields better toddy, but with lower quantity. It's a balancing act!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343700/extras/Locals.png?t=1681847013\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343700/extras/Npcshowcase.gif?t=